To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private BalanceOfPower _bop;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_bop = BOP(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_bop.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "balanceofpower", _bop.Current.Value);
}
